pageContext.claim: “MS-13, horrible gangs, we're getting them out by the thousands but our job would be so much easier if we had what we need on border security, border safety.”
pageContext.analysis: A range of data shows Trump’s crackdown on MS-13 has had a discernible impact. But there’s nothing showing that “thousands and thousands” of the gang’s members have been deported or imprisoned since the president took office. Instead, it's in the "hundreds and hundreds" ballpark.
